    <item>
      <title>Authoring The Redaction History</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/my-writeups/en/post/authoring-redaction-history/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hotrungdan3007@gmail.com (niddalA)</author>
      <dc:creator>niddalA</dc:creator>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/my-writeups/en/post/authoring-redaction-history/</guid>
      <description>How to set up the redaction history in Hugo Brewm theme</description>
      <content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;The redaction history functionality enables you to track and communicate content modifications to readers.&#xA;Within the post&amp;rsquo;s front matter, you can specify details such as &lt;code&gt;editor&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;reviewer&lt;/code&gt;, and include explanatory notes (&lt;code&gt;note&lt;/code&gt;) about the changes made.&#xA;This feature requires manual configuration in the post&amp;rsquo;s front matter section.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;table style=&#34;border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;2&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;3&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;4&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;5&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;6&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;7&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;8&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-toml&#34; data-lang=&#34;toml&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;+++&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;title&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Authoring The Redaction History&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;history&lt;/span&gt; = [&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    {&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;2025-02-01&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;author&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Author Name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;reviewer&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Reviewer Name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;note&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Example&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;},&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    {&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;2025-02-02&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;author&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Author Name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;editor&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Editor Name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;note&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Addendum (example)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;},&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    {&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;date&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;2025-02-03&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;note&lt;/span&gt; = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Errata (example)&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;},&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    ]&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;+++&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A chronological timeline displaying these information will appear under the article&amp;rsquo;s information section, as demonstrated in this example post.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;</content:encoded>
      <category>Authoring</category>
    </item>
